name: Lou Tuttle
tweet: I have difficulty envisioning a scenario in which the value of any smart contract platform is greater than the value of #Bitcoin for a sustained period of time. Platform users will only keep their 'gas tank' as full as it needs to be to get them from point A to point B.

name: Lou Tuttle
tweet: As is consistent in the traditional financial world, the TAM of monetary assets outweighs the TAM of utility-based assets, and the latter is a function of the former.  As a result, the ceiling for #Bitcoin relative to #Ether, #Solana, and the rest of the field is much higher.

name: Lou Tuttle
tweet: As #Bitcoin's monetary premium strengthens, I expect the same premium reflected in other cryptocurrencies to fall towards zero. This means the values of alternatives will be solely indicative of the utility they offer as a means of access to the capabilities of smart contracts.

name: Lou Tuttle
tweet: It is my opinion that #Bitcoin's irreplicable levels of decentralization and it's transparent and predictable monetary policy give it the best shot at retaining a long term monetary premium.
